la lettre suivera pr premiere aussi bost qu'on aura advis des fraises a veni le
selon quon a demande car i'ay voulu disputer le compte qu'on a fait, et j'auray
soing de minager vre intrest, si i'auvois seeu que cette malieur auroit
arrive iaurois donné ordre a un aultre amis pour honnorer la lettre pour mon
t

Pence mj last of 4 cur rec yours of 29 past, I have shipped yo. 2 packs
of tyhes tre first cur & indeed Jacob van herentals mode such I laste
that he was the 7h att brudges & onles the judaine frost ofe solud
have been with you are now butt such thinges can not behelped, to
send suck pakes expressely downes, will cost & come to great charges
besides not greater haste could have been made then van herentals did.
as to the great lead 3 seales & I 3 seales to bee risen please to
take novice, that the 2 packes you hed before these I have bought
of a neccessibated man & much under the cur prixe, so as are thes
3 last paesces, to mory in consideration the thread is risen about
20 p.S & therefore I am coufident noman shall send onney
